Hey, i read everywhere people are searching for Blank server sources so i want to make one, but i can't do it on my own, so i need some help
Also i want to make 2 versions *first 1 but if it works maybee a V2
V1:
things it will NOT get 1: No commands 2: No npc's 3: No SILAB STUFF 4: no portals 5: no quests 6: no standard characters in Characters map
Things it WILL get 1: homeplace: Edgeville 2: wilderness on the STANDARD locations, *EDITABLE* 3: All skills working
V2:
Same as V1 but with some extra's *new things in red*
things it will NOT get 1: No commands 2: No npc's 3: No SILAB STUFF 4: no portals 5: no quests 6: no standard characters in Characters map
Things it WILL get 1: homeplace: Edgeville 2: wilderness on the STANDARD locations, *EDITABLE* 3: All skills working / skillcapes (4: maybee summoning)5: Clan chat *always usefull* (Clanwars if possible) 6: Grand exange *only if i find a VERY GOOD TUT* Something i forgot?
tell me!
EXTRA: Downloads will come here if i finished I will put a little tut in the source for how to change homecity, and adding commands etc.
